@startuml Final Asset Saving

participant "template-service /\nvideo-editor" as GEN
participant "media-ingest\n(MinIO)" as MI
participant "RabbitMQ" as RMQ
participant "userservice" as US
participant "publisher" as PUB
participant "Frontend" as FE

GEN -> MI: upload final video/image
MI --> GEN: mediaId

GEN -> RMQ: AssetGenerated {mediaId, projectId, userId, type=final}
RMQ -> US: consume event
US -> US: CREATE GeneratedAsset (type=final)

note over FE,PUB: Пользователь решает опубликовать
FE -> PUB: POST /publications {assetId, ...}
PUB -> PUB: CREATE PublicationRecord {assetId}
note over PUB: assetId — просто ссылка,\nPUB не владеет ассетом

@enduml
